T|30 ·|0|A people/contacts directory. Appears as people-page.md in the creator's own Briefings folder (screenshot 181510).
T|30 ·|1|
T|Purp|0|A directory of the humans in the owner's world — partners, clients, leads, and collaborators — distinct from the ag (which live in ag/Org Chart). It's the human counterpart to the ag roster, and the relationship layer behind the Inbox and Consulting CRM.
T|Purp|1|
T|What|0|Contact records w/ relationship status, associated workspace, and history — the same kind of data the Inbox surfaces in its "What we know abt [sender]" panel (e.g. Maria Solano: warm prospect, ~€5k, language preferences, recent threads).
T|What|1|Likely links each person to their deals (Consulting CRM), their threads (Inbox), and any projects they're attached to (e.g. partner logins per workspace).
T|What|2|Pulls contact memory from the sb-backed memory sy.
T|What|3|
T|Rela|0|Underpins em Inbox (25) contact intelligence and Consulting CRM (23) leads.
T|Rela|1|Connects to the partner-login md in Workspaces & ds sy (26).
